{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846895059,"sessionID":"ses_28749eaf6ffebPa8vhmVB5f8vi","part":{"id":"prt_d78b92d88001wbiVccY7OYDm71","messageID":"msg_d78b7f045001ZABJVw38EHEMeI","sessionID":"ses_28749eaf6ffebPa8vhmVB5f8vi","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-19e7a6d867a844cd8a3efc801198772b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md","content":"# AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Core Types & Configuration (ST-1)\n\n- [x] **T1.1**: Define error types (`ValidationError`, `NotFoundError`, `InternalError`, `ServiceUnavailableError`, `ConflictError`)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager -run TestErrorTypes -v`\n- [x] **T1.2**: Define `ErrorResponse` and `SuccessResponse` structs\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T1.3**: Implement `HandleError` function for HTTP error responses\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go -run TestHandleError -v`\n- [x] **T1.4**: Define `DeletionReason` enum constants\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDetermineDeletionReason -v`\n- [x] **T1.5**: Define `Config` struct with HTTP server parameters\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go -run TestDefaultConfig -v`\n- [x] **T1.6**: Define `LifecycleConfig` struct with TTL/idle timeout settings\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestDefaultLifecycleConfig -v`\n- [x] **T1.7**: Define constants (SandboxGVR, SandboxClaimGVR, labels, annotations)\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/defaults_test.go -run TestGVRConstants -v`\n\n### Phase 2: Store Implementation (ST-2)\n\n- [x] **T2.1**: Implement `Store` interface with CRUD methods\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -v`\n- [x] **T2.2**: Implement `MemoryStore` with sync.RWMutex\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestMemoryStore -v`\n- [x] **T2.3**: Implement `ListExpiredSandboxes` with time-based filtering\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestListExpired -v`\n- [x] **T2.4**: Implement `ListInactiveSandboxes` with LastActivity filtering\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestListInactive -v`\n- [x] **T2.5**: Implement expiration index for efficient cleanup\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/store_test.go -run TestExpirationIndex -v`\n\n### Phase 3: Kubernetes Client (ST-3)\n\n- [x] **T3.1**: Implement `K8sClient` struct with dynamic/client-go clients\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestNewK8sClient -v`\n- [x] **T3.2**: Implement `ClientCache` for token-scoped dynamic clients\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestClientCache -v`\n- [x] **T3.3**: Implement `StartInformers` and `WaitForCacheSync`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestInformers -v`\n- [x] **T3.4**: Implement `PodLister` accessor\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client_test.go -run TestPodLister -v`\n- [x] **T3.5**: Implement `Informers` wrapper struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go -v`\n- [ ] **T3.6**: Fix `TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout` test failure\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/informers_test.go -run TestInformers_WaitForCacheSyncTimeout -v`\n\n### Phase 4: Lifecycle Manager (ST-4)\n\n- [x] **T4.1**: Implement `SandboxLifecycleManager` struct\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go -run TestNewSandbox